Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.21,0:01:01.57,opjap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)}Just now　この手の中で　熱く輝け
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.44,0:01:14.25,opjap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)}One in a seven billion の憂鬱
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.43,0:01:19.81,opjap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)}Someday 世界が終わる日が　来たって
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.95,0:01:25.01,opjap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)}So，What？　1ミリの悔いもない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.18,0:01:30.73,opjap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)}Say， yeah！！　一筋に走る流れ星
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.91,0:01:33.39,opjap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)}鼓動ドキドキ止まれ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.55,0:01:38.14,opjap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)}迷いも全部　蹴っ飛ばせ！！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.33,0:01:43.66,opjap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)}宇宙に　抱かれし　蒼い地球
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.82,0:01:48.93,opjap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)}いつも心に描く　エリシオン
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.08,0:01:54.29,opjap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)}過去も未来も　自分が創る
