Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.06,0:21:58.01,edjap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正義の剣は折れ 無機質に転がった
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.28,0:22:03.38,edjap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,支えてた自分 reasonとか 見えなくなってしまうの?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.59,0:22:08.55,edjap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,左手で掴んでも 右手からこぼれて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.94,0:22:13.64,edjap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泣いてなんかいないのに 霞んで行く情景
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.80,0:22:18.93,edjap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ゆらり揺れて 惑わす世界はきっと
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.13,0:22:23.39,edjap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未来切符を探してる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.12,0:22:29.44,edjap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鈍い音に 焦らされるように
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.61,0:22:33.62,edjap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走り出さなきゃ ゴールはない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.84,0:22:39.94,edjap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,future is serious! future is serious!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.15,0:22:45.35,edjap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,なんで、どうして、心が邪魔をするの?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.51,0:22:47.72,edjap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,future is serious!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.93,0:22:57.13,edjap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,何十回繰り返しても 戸惑いを振り払って
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.40,0:23:07.21,edjap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,立ち上がる まだ夢を見たまま…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.63,0:00:21.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這 這樣就可以了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.63,0:00:23.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,內衣也脫了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.61,0:00:26.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,內 內 內衣也要脫嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.55,0:00:27.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快給我脫
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.15,0:00:28.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,/OP
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.21,0:02:11.42,bt,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(140,0)}第4話 「無法停止的{\1c&2338ab&}超{\1c&HFFFFFF&}振動」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.51,0:02:24.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優米爾大人 這是？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.76,0:02:26.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是你即將穿在身上的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.94,0:02:28.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超振動裝備
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.70,0:02:31.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問 超振動裝備是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.96,0:02:34.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,依靠超振動水晶的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.20,0:02:35.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,展開特殊的力場
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.20,0:02:38.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將敵人的攻擊全部彈開
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.75,0:02:40.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,究極的鎧甲
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.94,0:02:43.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要 要 要我當鬥士什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.64,0:02:44.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.42,0:02:46.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可是為了你家人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.03,0:02:53.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實驗要開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.03,0:02:54.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.32,0:03:08.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這身鎧甲的特點是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.37,0:03:12.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對手的攻擊越強 水晶的振動也會越強
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.83,0:03:14.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從而產生強大的力場
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.05,0:03:17.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我該做什麼好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.97,0:03:20.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在那老實站著就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.70,0:03:33.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我上了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.48,0:03:53.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是偉大的煉金術師·希昂的魔導石
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.25,0:03:59.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而能承受住這份力量的這副身體也真了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.77,0:04:01.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是有點太敏感了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.04,0:04:05.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.11,0:04:10.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,集鋼鐵山所有的知識和技術於一身
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.66,0:04:12.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大陸最強鬥士計劃
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.35,0:04:17.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於 其第一號實驗體完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.80,0:04:20.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超振動戰乙女·美莉姆
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.84,0:04:28.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,號外 號外
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.71,0:04:31.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滿版都是大事件的報道哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.73,0:04:34.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在各地被目擊到的謎之光的真相
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.08,0:04:37.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是否從月亮降臨的最強鬥士呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.19,0:04:41.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡里巴拉的深處 濃霧的密林中
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.54,0:04:44.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,探險隊捕獲了傳說中的珍獸
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.17,0:04:48.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 竟竟竟竟竟然
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.55,0:04:50.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女王大人的私生子疑雲
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.79,0:04:53.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷鳴之夜出生的三胞胎姐妹
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.16,0:04:56.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欲知詳情
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.86,0:04:58.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請君解囊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.38,0:05:07.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老百姓就是喜歡看那種大事件 溫迪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.65,0:05:11.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以把這些提供給他們
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.40,0:05:13.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是我的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.01,0:05:16.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然也說不上是真實的報道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.94,0:05:21.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 要早點到蓋納斯去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.35,0:05:22.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到美莉姆才行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.31,0:05:28.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是 什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.84,0:05:33.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總算追上你了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.84,0:05:36.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,預言中出現的「命運之人」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.69,0:05:40.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該死的通緝犯 乖乖就範吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.90,0:05:47.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後就差「偶然」發生的「命運的再會」了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.07,0:05:53.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.99,0:05:57.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身體裡長出了奇怪的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.47,0:05:59.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能讓我採訪下麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.70,0:05:59.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.55,0:06:06.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.44,0:06:09.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.95,0:06:12.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.59,0:06:14.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.03,0:06:15.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可疑的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.67,0:06:18.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是通緝犯的同夥嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.14,0:06:22.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為為為什麼會變成這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.42,0:06:25.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,究極的鎧甲？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.35,0:06:30.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.49,0:06:31.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也有配套的武器哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.52,0:06:33.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,預測敵人的行動
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.18,0:06:36.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自動攻擊敵人的究極武器
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.13,0:06:39.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超振動劍·無限利刃以及
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.13,0:06:39.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（Infinite Slasher）
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.10,0:06:41.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超振動盾
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.93,0:06:51.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 請鑒賞我之計劃的成果吧 女王陛下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.01,0:06:54.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女王陛下？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.75,0:06:58.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成果啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.28,0:07:02.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得這玩意在實戰中可沒什麼用
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.50,0:07:05.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾麗娜 你要來試試嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.41,0:07:07.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挺有趣嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.83,0:07:10.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.44,0:07:14.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平身
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.34,0:07:15.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.83,0:07:50.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃了姐姐大人一劍還能毫髮無傷
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.76,0:07:59.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 我已經站不住了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.56,0:08:07.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不在這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.74,0:08:15.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尤依特 已經安全了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.62,0:08:19.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥竟然是女人 真讓我嚇了一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.30,0:08:22.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以不要再叫我哥哥了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.65,0:08:24.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會改的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.95,0:08:28.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為事到如今再改稱呼又不合理
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.48,0:08:31.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.58,0:08:34.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想死你了 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.22,0:08:36.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.64,0:08:37.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.80,0:08:45.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隨你便吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.98,0:08:50.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我啊 還以為再也見不到哥哥了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.16,0:08:53.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那一天
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.70,0:08:58.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我離開克萊因城堡的那一天
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.67,0:09:07.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明想向你好好道別的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.08,0:09:09.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卻沒能見到哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.92,0:09:15.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.31,0:09:17.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.45,0:09:21.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為現在和你重逢了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.17,0:09:23.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尤依特
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.27,0:09:34.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又要去找姐姐大人了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.86,0:09:45.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要我當鬥士什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.31,0:09:47.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.60,0:09:49.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那身鎧甲只有我才能脫掉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.22,0:09:57.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優米爾大人 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.36,0:10:00.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在不幹的話 錢就泡湯了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.76,0:10:08.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這才對
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.14,0:10:12.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優米爾大人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.14,0:10:15.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事 慌慌張張的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.73,0:10:16.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.93,0:10:18.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從返回的偵察隊中
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.64,0:10:22.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得到了在索羅爾附近 目擊到安妮洛特的報告
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.81,0:10:26.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想不到這麼快就有實戰測試的機會
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.49,0:10:30.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前那個機器人及其主人也在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.96,0:10:34.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尤依特？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.55,0:10:40.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那要趕快做好出擊的準備了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.14,0:11:07.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你逃不出我的五指山
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.34,0:11:25.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我的確需要錢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.58,0:11:29.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但為此要跟尤依特戰鬥的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.94,0:11:30.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是美鬥士
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.97,0:11:31.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快讓路
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.59,0:11:33.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真美麗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.46,0:11:39.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好疼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.59,0:11:59.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿著這鎧甲 身體不能隨心所欲地活動
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.46,0:12:01.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.17,0:12:22.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道到底該怎麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.64,0:12:26.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上帝將拯救所有人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.97,0:12:28.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請說出你的煩惱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.54,0:12:30.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.52,0:12:41.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論你逃到哪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.65,0:12:46.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都可以根據鎧甲上水晶發出的波動追蹤到
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.60,0:12:53.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 其實我…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.05,0:12:57.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.92,0:12:59.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.33,0:13:11.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.49,0:13:15.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.94,0:13:24.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這難道是 惡魔附體？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.21,0:13:27.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是因此而祈求上帝的庇護嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.25,0:13:29.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.45,0:13:31.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,違抗上帝的惡魔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.93,0:13:36.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上帝啊 請用您的愛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.77,0:13:38.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用神之光照耀她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.60,0:13:39.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救贖她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.51,0:13:45.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣做的話 會變得更激烈的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.33,0:13:48.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惡魔在抵抗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.60,0:13:53.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡的惡魔 從她身上滾出去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.94,0:14:02.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請不要再打了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.57,0:14:06.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論如何都無法驅逐的話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.11,0:14:10.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就將你視為異端 施以火刑
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.49,0:14:15.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.94,0:14:21.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來在這
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.21,0:14:25.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把她還給我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.51,0:14:36.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請等等
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.74,0:14:37.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.47,0:14:40.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是神聖的教會
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.02,0:14:43.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有中央教王廳的許可
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.21,0:14:45.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你為所欲為的話我會很困擾
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.64,0:14:48.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是異端審問官·斯琪大人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.84,0:14:50.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那能請你高抬貴手
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.13,0:14:53.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把她還給我們嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.01,0:15:02.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美莉姆 給我過來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.57,0:15:09.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.50,0:15:14.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要出擊了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.32,0:15:18.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去擊敗反抗女王的安妮洛特
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.21,0:15:20.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.21,0:15:22.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安妮洛特
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.92,0:15:27.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在此分別吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.54,0:15:30.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥又要去別的地方嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.64,0:15:30.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.53,0:15:33.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你打算怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.51,0:15:37.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要去女王的首都·蓋納斯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.88,0:15:39.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去蓋納斯…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.21,0:15:44.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要去找被鋼鐵參謀·優米爾帶走的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.26,0:15:48.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還必須奪回被偷走的媽媽的魔導石
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.24,0:15:53.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路上小心
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.74,0:15:54.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.82,0:15:57.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.06,0:16:01.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次再見吧 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.99,0:16:18.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,礙事的傢伙走了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.12,0:16:22.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這回終於可以跟姐姐來個「命運的再會」了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.65,0:16:58.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.53,0:17:05.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是贏了你 弟弟們就可以填飽肚子了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.75,0:17:10.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.34,0:17:15.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了弟弟們
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.39,0:17:19.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請幫幫我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.49,0:17:32.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不快點投降的話 不然的話
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.18,0:17:35.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.10,0:17:39.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.78,0:17:44.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我越使勁她力氣就更大
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.05,0:17:52.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是找到美莉姆 就和她一起吃頓美味大餐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.48,0:17:56.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天賺了不少 預算足夠了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.18,0:18:04.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時候沒機會交給哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.52,0:18:09.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想著總有一天要給她 一直帶在身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.41,0:18:17.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山茶花的花語是「強大與驕傲」
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.40,0:18:20.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和哥哥真襯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.78,0:18:36.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再繼續的話 我就要
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.95,0:18:43.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忍不了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.54,0:18:49.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.35,0:18:51.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.90,0:18:55.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.03,0:19:06.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於該命運的邂逅了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.91,0:19:15.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.15,0:19:19.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,溫迪 要救哥哥了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.50,0:19:28.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.09,0:19:31.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火箭飛拳
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.44,0:19:41.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美莉姆
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.92,0:19:47.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我現在就來 姐姐大人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.68,0:20:00.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尤依特
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.46,0:20:04.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼美莉姆會…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.13,0:20:13.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼我在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.42,0:20:24.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那名鬥士到底…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.23,0:20:29.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她就是我正在找的朋友 美莉姆
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.36,0:20:32.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尤依特的朋友？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.68,0:20:35.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正的美莉姆不是那樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.50,0:20:38.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她既關心家人又溫柔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.57,0:20:43.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那人一定是知道了她生活拮据 才強迫她
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.83,0:20:47.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偷了魔導石的 也一定是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.86,0:20:51.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那股不可思議的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.98,0:20:55.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或許與希昂大人的魔導石有關聯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.81,0:21:04.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全都是為了這個目的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.56,0:21:08.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鋼鐵參謀·優米爾
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.06,0:21:12.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對饒不了你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.98,0:21:23.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出發吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.17,0:21:26.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去蓋納斯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.37,0:21:30.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,/ED
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.04,0:23:15.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鋼鐵參謀·優米爾大人竟然對我的身體做那種實驗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.80,0:23:19.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且我早說了我當不了鬥士了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.44,0:23:22.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安妮洛特姐姐大人不快點投降的話
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.34,0:23:25.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就再也忍不住了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.06,0:23:30.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但為了媽媽她們 必須要努力
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.83,0:23:33.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一話 蓋納斯城的秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.57,0:23:35.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騙人 那裡綁成那樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.95,0:23:37.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道龍戰士是...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.80,0:23:39.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超級受虐狂嗎


